h/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdecd5555-6b02-4b43-a933-3e5959bcea42_768x808.jpeg" width="684" height="719.625" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/decd5555-6b02-4b43-a933-3e5959bcea42_768x808.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:808,&quot;width&quot;:768,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:684,&quot;bytes&quot;:86730,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdecd5555-6b02-4b43-a933-3e5959bcea42_768x808.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdecd5555-6b02-4b43-a933-3e5959bcea42_768x808.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdecd5555-6b02-4b43-a933-3e5959bcea42_768x808.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdecd5555-6b02-4b43-a933-3e5959bcea42_768x808.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/spurred-by-federal-legislation-new-industrial-investments-are-reaching-a-wide-swath-of-the-country/">布鲁金斯学会</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>一些进步派专家声称这是<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2023/07/20/bidenomics-rust-belt-trump-2024-sun-belt/">明智的选举策略</a>，因为亚利桑那州和佐治亚州是2024年重要的摇摆州<a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2023/07/biden-economic-industrial-investment-red-state-beneficiaries/674633/">。其他人则担心</a>投资集中在工会实力较弱的州将降低产业政策支持工会权力的程度。但说实话，我认为这张地图主要只是反映了成本而不是政治。</p><p>请记住，CHIPS 法案和 IRA 的最大作用是向私人投资者提供巨额补贴。实际政府投资有所增加，但尚未蓬勃发展： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:1318,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:52139,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f22d0fe-b75e-41a3-ad07-b6282cce14eb_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这些政策提供的补贴不分地区。所以我们真正看到的是<em>私营公司更愿意把工厂建在哪里</em>。这将取决于一系列因素，例如土地购置成本、廉价住房的可用性、天气、劳动力的教育水平、劳动法规等等。它还将取决于当地的集群效应——加州有硅谷，因此可能很难让顶尖技术工人放弃 <a href="https://www.levels.fyi/?compare=Google,Facebook,Microsoft&amp;track=Software%20Engineer">高额技术工资</a>去芯片厂工作。</p><p>至于南方，我不会轻易认为是对工会不友好的政策推动了那里与中西部相比不成比例的投资。南方在这里根本没有太大的工资优势——佐治亚州和田纳西州的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_U.S._states_and_territories_by_median_wage_and_mean_wage">平均年薪</a>与威斯康星州和密歇根州大致相同。相反，我的直觉是，南方的优势可能是由于天气和建造新建筑的便利性的某种结合而产生的——这就是美国人<a href="https://www.pewtrusts.org/en/research-and-analysis/articles/2023/05/17/southern-states-gain-residents-the-fastest">普遍搬到那里</a>的原因。</p><p>但这里真正的信息是，我们不应该只看投资地图并假设它反映了基于地方的区域发展战略或拜登政府的选举政治。西部和新英格兰各州需要思考为什么很难在那里建工厂。</p><h4> 2.“煎锅图”只是通货膨胀图</h4><p>在推特上，经济学家亚历克斯·威廉姆斯（Alex Williams）展示了<a href="https://twitter.com/vebaccount/status/1685470963511508992">一堆“煎锅”图表，</a>引起了不小的轰动。 2008年金融危机和大衰退之后，许多经济指标——GDP、消费等——似乎永久下降。他们在经济衰退后恢复了增长，但并没有弥补失去的土地；长期趋势似乎正在向下转变。但疫情过后，许多指标似乎又回到了之前的趋势。例如，以下是 GDP 和消费： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3f005cb-b018-4891-9e3a-a2ec81d466d9_1553x895.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3f005cb-b018-4891-9e3a-a2ec81d466d9_1553x895.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3f005cb-b018-4891-9e3a-a2ec81d466d9_1553x895.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff3f005cb-b018-4891-9e3a-a2ec81d466d9_1553x895.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/